item.title: I am the new Bob Dylan
item.dc:creator: @LilXCj LilXCj
item.description:
@LilXCj wrote:

I wanna be the very best…
Like no one ever was.
To code games is my real test.
Debug them is my cause!
I will travel across the web.
Leeching some new designs.
This brand new game…
is a RuneScape Private Server!
MOPARSCAPE! (I will code them all!)
Notepad and me! (Leeching is my destiny!)
MOPARSCAPE!
Oh! You’re my best friend!
In my code I must defend!
(OBFUSCATE! I will protect it all!)
My code is so true!
My code is better than Stews! ((lolol R-S reference))
You teach me and I’ll leech you!
MOPARSCAPE!
GONNA CODE THEM ALL
GONNA LEECH THEM ALL
MOPARSCAPE!
